more passengers a day from downtown Los Angeles than Greyhound. Right, deputy 
unlocks holding cell in Men's Central. ; Photo, (Southland Edition) 'Nobody 
gets on the bus without being handcuffed -- nobody,' Deputy Brian Glennon says. 
RICK MEYER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
