<P>
DEPORTATION; ESPIONAGE -- USSR; ESPIONAGE -- ENGLAND; ENGLAND -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- USSR; ENGLANG -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; USSR -- GOVERNMENT 
OFFICIALS 
</P>
